title: Persona The Fool Sound Collection
description:
Blond guy: Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Blond guy: This place exist between dream and reality, Mind and matter.
Blond guy: My name is Wyll, I am delighted to make your acquaintance.
Wyll: As you can see, there is a Piano, A Guitar, A Drum set, And a few other instruments over there.
Wyll: You see, Our Band will be here in a while, You will wait for them to come, Will you?
Wyll: Just Download this Torrent and I'm sure they will be happy to play for you *chuckles*.
Wyll: Ah, I believe I neglected to explain about the Fool Sound Collection.
Wyll: it is the Ultimate Collection for Yu Narukami, Minato Arisato, And even Kotone Shiomi.
Wyll: I'm very sure it will be useful to you.
Wyll: that's all i have to say for now.
Wyll: 'Till we meet again, Farewell
